title: Taylor Swift Song Search
description: Compares songs with over one billion views and tells the user which Taylor Swift song is most similar to each using TF-IDF.

title: League of Legends Game Analysis
description: Assessed the impact of killing the first rift herald in competitive games from (2023-2024).

title: Climate in Major U.S. Cities
description: Produced a visualization to answer the question: “What does the make-up of average yearly rainfall look like for each city?”

title: KNN-Classifier for Daytime v.s. Nighttime pictures
description: Created a KNN-Classifier to classify different photos of either daytime or nighttime.

title: Predicting Player Salaries in the NBA
description: Created a model to predict NBA player salaries based on scoring and performance metrics.

title: Meteorite Analysis
description: Explored whether there is a trend in the median mass of meteorites over time for only the meteorites that were seen while falling since 1900 (including the year 1900).

title: Mouse Data Analysis
description: Created two visualizations. One was created in earnest to be informative and the other was created with the purpose of deceiving the reader.
